---
import siteData from '@/data/site.json';
---
<footer class="bg-[#fdfbf7] border-t border-[#ece8e1] py-12 mt-16">
  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 md:flex justify-between gap-8">
    <div class="pb-12">
      <h3 class="font-serif text-[#4a423d] font-bold mb-4">{siteData.title}</h3>
      <p class="text-sm text-[#7a726b] leading-relaxed">
        心と体のバランスを整え、<br>明日をもっと前向きに。
      </p>
    </div>
<div>
  <h3 class="font-serif text-[#4a423d] font-bold mb-4">メニュー</h3>
  <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-[#7a726b] md:flex gap-4">
    {siteData.navigation.links.map((link) => (
      <li>
        <a href={link.url} class="hover:text-[#4a423d] transition-colors">
          {link.label}
        </a>
      </li>
    ))}
  </ul>
</div>
  </div>

<div class="px-40">
    <ul class="flex justify-center gap-8 text-sm text-stone-500 mt-6 border-y-1 border-slate-200 py-6">
        <li><a href="/privacy-policy">プライバシーポリシー</a></li>
        <li><a href="/terms">免責事項</a></li>
    </ul>
</div>


      <div class="text-center text-sm text-[#7a726b] mt-6">
      <p>&copy; {new Date().getFullYear()} Spiritual Town</p>
    </div>
</footer>